name: EAGLEPROAI
0:
”Alexa, tell EAGLE PRO AI to turn on guest Wi-Fi.”
”Alexa, ask EAGLE PRO AI to tell me the guest Wi-Fi password.”
”Alexa, tell EAGLE PRO AI to reboot the router.”
skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: eagle pro a. i.
Developer Terms of Use
des:
EAGLE PRO AI skills for Amazon Alexa now lets you control your home network with the power of your voice. It's now possible to manage your home Wi-Fi without lifting a finger.
 - Enable or disable your Guest Wi-Fi quickly when you throw your next party. 
 - Obtain your guest network name and password immediately, whenever you need it.
 - Reboot your router without having to push any buttons.
 - Carry out a firmware upgrade to ensure you have the latest features.
 - Ask for recent weekly report
 
Before you begin, you will need:
 - An Alexa Voice Service enabled device.
 - An Alexa-supported EAGLE PRO AI Router. 
 - The EAGLE PRO AI app installed on your mobile device with a registered D-Link account.

Devices with D-Link Wi-Fi App support should use D-Link Wi-Fi skills.
